                Silvanab<lb break="no" n="2"/>us <expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aemil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Fronto <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In zwei Teile gebrochen. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. (B): Kubitschek: keine Zeilenfälle angegeben; Z. 1/2: [Silva]na[bus], nach der Zeichnung Silvana[b]/us; CIL 03, 14355, 11; AE 1900: Silvana[b]/us; AE 1900: Z. 2: sacr(um).</p>
            </div>
